SourceString: An sinister weapon premanently burning with unholy fire.
The venomous tip of the lord of stingrays\' tail, which slew the hero Odysseus.
A tapering point with a singular purpose.
A small club used for knocking victims unconscious.
A unique weapon, tempered by Zeus\'s thunderbolt. It crackles with energy.
An implement for doing things right.
The blade seems to only partially exist in this world.
Taken from the foot of a metallic bird.
This strange knife is covered in black ink.
The blade was once shattered, to bury any memory of the dark role it played.
A magical ice crystal that radiates biting cold.
A shining blade that wounds the spirit as much as the body.
A sword of superb quality, finely honed and well balanced.
A relic from a place of legends past.
They say Asklepios used this on his patients. It now serves a more gruesome purpose.
A sword made for magic users rather than warriors.
The sword of the heroic spirit you met on the beach.
Created by a king to break a nymph\'s spell, this sword sparks fear in the hearts of magic-users.
Theia, mother of Helios and Selene, is the titan of light and brilliance.
The bloodthirst of the mighty centaur warrior still lingers in this Khopesh.
A cursed sword from the land of the midnight sun.
A grim remnant from the fall of Sparta.
An insidious weapon designed to freeze and shatter living beings.
An axe fashioned from razor-sharp crab claws.
A well-honed blade coated in poison.
When rats were breedng in the sewers, Tegean citizens developed an unsettling mixture of volatile poisons.
A hungry spirit was bound within this weapon.
This coral is hard enough to shatter bone.
Block crush and impale, all with one handy tool.
Emits a cloud of spores when shaken.
Giving humans fire elevated them above any other of the gods\' creations.
While ingenuity ran in the family, Perdix had a special interest in iron and magnetism.
A club made of junk, seemingly for a creature the size of a cyclops.
This massive axe that once hung above the entrance to the Labyrinth in Knossos.
A large axe once gifted by Zeus to the king of Thracia.
The flames of Hephaistos\'s forge still burn in this weapon\'s blade.
For centuries the creature lay in wait, lurking in its prison of stone, until you slew it.
When Demeter lifted the eternal winter, only this axe remained.
Legend says that the strength of great heroes past lingers in this mighty weapon.
A dark aura surrounds this old dory.
A weird magical spear used in ichthian rituals.
A spear that always strikes true, enchanted by Artemis as a gift to Orion.
A masterpiece from the Temple of Kheimon, prime purveyor of cold-enchanted weapons and silent guardsmen.
The legendary Amazon queen inspired her followers by leading from the front.
A weapon enchanted with the power of wind and lightning.
A bow that hits with unusually explosive force.
Sometimes quantity is the answer after all.
The string of this bow is a magical band of shifting colors.
A staff infused with the very essence of fire.
A vined staff, sacred to Dionysos.
Crafting Zeus\' thunderbolt took many failed attempts, some more promising than others.
A staff that projects blunt force, useful to settle scholarly disagreements.
Holding this staff fills you with the vim of a new day.
Sharp poisoned spikes dampen the appetite of most would-be predators.
A mystical shield bearing the symbols of Hekate.
The iconic shield of Spartan warrior, rarely found without its owner.
The bigger the creature, the greater the glory.
A large embossed bowl depicting mythical scenes of Glaukos and the people of Pyrgos.
A shield fashioned from a sturdy crab shell.
The iron seal of a veteran commander.
A fine gold ring with a multitude of small colorful stones.
Touched by Strength itself, the plain looking metal emenates an aura of might and fury.
Wearing this amulet makes you feel refreshed and energized.
A cursed amulet that once held the image of a dear spouse.
A charm fashioned from an owl\'s talon.
Crabs seem to sense that the bearer of this trophy is a threat.
A concoction that slowly shifts between three colors.
A storm of radiant energy rages inside.
Looks dark and gooey, but smells enticing...
A mysterious glow emanates from powerful gear hidden within.
A piece of a relic. Which will it be?
A piece of a rare relic. Which will it be?
A piece of a charm. Which will it be?
A piece of a rare charm. Which will it be?
